description:
Install the package:
$ dotnet new -i Genocs.CleanArchitecture.Template::3.0.0

The full clean project:
$ dotnet new cleanarchitecture
releaseNotes:
- Relesase 3.0.0:
  Added list of events
  
- Clean Architecture Principles Documentation
- .NET8
- Swashbuckle 5 
- Entity Framework Core 5
- Enterprice Service Bus
summary: A .NET template following the Clean Architecture Style, DDD and Separation of Concerns in Domain, Application, Infrastructure and UI. Separated host for WebApi and ServiceBus. Docker compose debugging support provided as well.
title: Genocs - Clean Code Template
